page.title: 03MYSELF BY TRACY HULL
page.content: HELLO MY NAME IS TRACY ANN HULL. MY AGE S 10.I HAVE 5 PEOPLE IN MY FAMILY, MY MUM,DAD,SISTER MICHELLE AND BROTHER DANIEL.I DON'T ALWAYS GET ON WITH MY SISTER BUT I CAN GET ON WITH MY BROTHER I GET UP AT 7.45 WHEN ITS SCHOOL,BUT AT WEEKENDS I GET UP AT 8.30.ON SCHOOL DAYS I GO TO BED AT 8.45-9.00 AND AT WEEKENDS ABOUT 9.30. I DONÂ£T GET POCKET MONEY BUT MONEY FOR SWEETS AND DISCOS. IN MY SPARE TIME I RIDE MY PONY OR TIDY MY GARDEN.I SPEND MY MONEY ON SWEETS, TOYS AND PLANTS.MY FAVOURITE FOODS ARE CHIPS,SAUSAGES AND MEAT.I GO ON HOLIDAY EACH YEAR,USUALLY TO GREAT YARMOUTH BUT THIS YEAR ITÂ£S TO DEVON.I GO TO CHAPEL EVERY SUNDAY,AT CHAPEL I GO TO SUNDAY SCHOOL.I BELONG TO THE JUNIOR TIMES IN THE EAST ANGLIAN AND BROWNIES,BALLET AND GYMNASTICS HELD IN NEARBY VILLAGES. I THINK I LEAD AN INTERESTING LIFE.
